                                                <h1>Executive Summary</h1>
                                                <h2 class="all-caps">Introduction</h2>
                                                <p>Hilton Hotels &amp; Resorts Lobby Design Narrative provides guidance to achieve a consistent on-brand Guest experience while maintaining an identity for each property. Hilton understands that not every existing property has the ability to embrace each and every aspect of the Ideal Hilton Lobby as would a new hotel; but this narrative helps guide owners and designers of <a href="#" class="inline-link">existing hotel</a> properties to: </p>
                                                <ul class="dashed">
                                                    <li><strong class="all-caps">EVALUATE THE MERITS OF THEIR EXISTING HOTEL LOBBIES</strong></li>
                                                    <li><strong class="all-caps">DISCOVER THE DIFFERENCES between their existing space and the Ideal Hilton Lobby.</strong></li>
                                                    <li><strong class="all-caps">ESTABLISH A MASTER PLAN</strong></li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
